{"tid":1497522,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"要北上做嘢的電話","createTime":"2019-08-23T04:03:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T04:30:41.000Z","uid":298802,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3af084acd27eb0be8f10aa60aabe35af7fb1ad57","tid":1497522,"uid":298802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:03:19.000Z","msg":"買部電話<br />\n將所有數據資料傳送到新機<br />\n新電話唔裝FB TG INSG<br />\n必裝 Whatspp QQ WECHART 淘寶 支付寶 + 6 7個遊戲APP<br />\n把不必要的資料DEL 記得清咗BROWSER 記錄 書簽<br />\n百度做首頁<br />\n制做兩三日通話記錄 WECHART 記錄<br />\n回港再登入自己電話 WHATSAPP重新認證<br />\n<br />\n咁樣佢只睇相薄 同會問你點解無FB 你答大陸工作 平時都用唔到所以無戶口 只需半個鐘走得 <br />\n唔好唔帶電話 或者部機空白 <br />\n因為我今個星期二過關 公司個後生仔因為電話無料 公安打算入房查資料 我哋班老鬼話佢新嚟 部電話公司剛俾佢 先放行<br />\n<br />\n盡量唔過羅湖 羅湖抽查比較大 改道落馬洲<br />\n盡可能上午過關<br />\n<br />\n記住落嚟都會查<br />\n<br />\n從雨傘開始咁做 查電話亦是當年開始"},{"pid":"664e8b071edf1f6df8ec6d81df52588eb60976da","tid":1497522,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:04:37.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">612 721 811<br />\n<br />\n823 人鏈<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;823 23:59死線&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1494948\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1494948</a><br />\n<br />\n824 朝早7點機場<br />\n<br />\n824 晏晝1點觀塘<br />\n<br />\n825 荃葵青<br />\n <br />\n831 中聯辦<br />\n<br />\n9月頭三罷同塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">不分和勇！永不割席！<br />\n<br />\n香港人 請為自由而戰<br />\nFight for freedom, Stand with Hong Kong</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong></span><br />\nLiberate Hong Kong, Revolution of our time